arStrings.szText: {c_gold}Use: {/c}Increases Resistance to All Elements by {c_yellow}+10%{/c}, Maximum Resistance to All Elements by {c_yellow}+1%{/c}, and Armor by {c_yellow}+150{/c} for every nearby player and increases Experience by {c_yellow}5%{/c}. Lasts 20 minutes.
This is a type II incense. Only one Incense of a type may be active at a time. Experience Bonus does not stack with other Incenses.
